
*** general ***

author   = Agrammon Group
date     = 2026-05-04
taxonomy = PlantProduction::CropResidues
gui	 = PlantProduction::CropResidues,Pflanzenbau::Ernterückstände,Production végétale::Résidus végétaux,Plant production::Crop residues

+short

Computes the annual NH3 emission from crop residues.
	
+description 

Computes the annual NH3 emission from crop residues.

